          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>A curated library of prompts for various AI image generation tools</li>
            <li>Search and filtering capabilities</li>
            <li>The ability to save favorites locally</li>
            <li>A platform for community contributions via GitHub</li>
          </ul>
