          <p>
            The prompts and content on AwesomePrompts are provided under the <a href="https://github.com/samuxbuilds/awesome-prompts/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 hover:underline">MIT License</a>. You are free to:
