          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Use, copy, and modify the prompts for personal or commercial purposes</li>
            <li>Distribute and share the prompts</li>
            <li>Contribute your own prompts to the collection</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            When contributing, you affirm that you have the right to share the content and agree to license it under the same MIT License.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">5. AI-Generated Content Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            The prompts provided are templates for AI image generation. We do not control the output generated by AI tools using these prompts. Users are responsible for:
